<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/box/{scope}/file/{file_id}/generated/{generated_type}/raw"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Retrieves and responds with the raw contents of a specific generated file. This should be used when serving the file up from the browser.
Sets the Content-Disposition header to display the file inline so that this URL can be used in pdf viewers.
